enftun (0.9.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ David R. Bild ]
  * readme: add install instructions for Ubuntu Bionic

  [ Daniel Berliner ]
  * Rename SCM to HSS

  [ David R. Bild ]
  * release v0.7.3

  [ Daniel Berliner ]
  * Load tss2 blob file via tpm2tss engine

  [ Zane Beckwith ]
  * .docker: Use buster, not stretch.
  * .docker: Install libtss2-dev package, for the TPM TSS2 implementation.
  * .travis: Use Buster docker image (v0.2.1)
  * xtt: Use xtt v0.11 and xaptum-tpm v1.0, which requires new TSS library.
  * README: Bump xtt requirement to 0.11.0.
  * README: Mention libjansson dependency.
  * tcp: Formatting, to satisfy clang-format check.

  [ Daniel Berliner ]
  * Add TPM parameters to enftun_xtt_handshake

  [ Zane Beckwith ]
  * tls_tpm: No longer need ifdef to avoid xtt+tpm.
  * xtt: Save private key as TPM blob file (and create cert accordingly).

  [ Daniel Berliner ]
  * config: Make tpm own section.
  * keygen: Create KEYGEN_USE_TPM CMake option.
  * keygen/tpm: Get init_tcti working, and a function for loading TPM keys
  * Allow either on-disk or TPM ECDSA keys.

  [ Zane Beckwith ]
  * keygen: Bring back linkage to libsodium.
  * combine tls_tpm engine init, and set TCTI config for engine.
  * Fix ordering of params in xtt.c TPM save_creds
  * Consolidate KEYGEN_USE_TPM into BUILD_TPM option.
  * config: Don't use tpm_password_len.
  * tpm: Fix tpm_password strlen call.

  [ David R. Bild ]
  * enftun: learn to display version number
  * release v0.8.0
  * xtt: zero the handshake and group contexts
  * release v0.8.1
  * config: remove ENF broker IPv6 address from defaults
  * release v0.8.2
  * xtt: fix code formatting
  * test/router: add support for IPv4 ICMP ping
  * filter: add helper filter for IPv4 packet type
  * filter: remove verbose log messages
  * config: add option to control IPv4 support
  * enftun: allow IPv4 through ingress and egress filters

  [ Zane Beckwith ]
  * xtt: Update to new XTT API for certificates.
  * Bump xtt requirement to >=0.12.0
  * release v0.8.3

  [ David R. Bild ]
  * ci: update dependencies in CI Docker image
  * ip: use netinet, not linux, header field names
  * keygen: flush stdout after prompt
  * test: copy all test files into build dir
  * heartbeat: simplify timers and scheduling
  * heartbeat: move settings into remote config section

  [ Kathryn Fejer ]
  * add separate ip address for the ENF router

  [ David R. Bild ]
  * context: refactor context initialization
  * tls: store fwmark in struct
  * all: clear all structs in init and free functions
  * conn_state: replace prepare/close with init/free

  [ Kathryn Fejer ]
  * conn_state: enable heartbeat

  [ David R. Bild ]
  * conn_state: send heartbeat on network changes
  * keygen: handle error in parsing config file
  * log: fix use of variable args
  * tls: properly clear OpenSSL error queue before calling new methods

  [ Zane Beckwith ]
  * icmp: Fix incorrect reference-to-pointer when computing ping checksum.

  [ David R. Bild ]
  * release v0.9.0

 -- David R. Bild <david.bild@xaptum.com>  Fri, 21 May 2021 04:53:27 +0000

